OS_FSControl 57 (&39)
#Parent OS_FSControl
=>	R0 =	57 (map out defect from large disc or image)
	R1 =	pointer to name of object
	R2 =	least significant word of defect address
	R3 =	most significant word of defect address

Maps out a defect from a large disc or image. This call is only supported on RISC OS 3.60 and later - if an error is returned try <OS_FSControl 42=>OS_FSControl42>.
